- help_us = '<h3>help us</h3> |
    <p>If you find this pod useful to you and make daily use of it, it makes me happy. :) But let\'s face it, running a bunch of servers doesn\'t |
    come without costs. Any donations are highly encouraged and will make sure that I can keep this pod running at full speed.</p> |
    <h3>other ways to help</h3> |
    <p>You don\'t need money to help running this pod. If you can do user interface design, write code or are just in general a creative person and want to help |
    push diaspora* forward, please check out the <a href="https://diasporafoundation.org/get_involved">how to get involved</a> page for ways to help. |
    Helping diaspora* directly helps this pod too! |
    <div> |
        <a class="btn btn-success" href="https://diasporafoundation.org/get_involved">Learn more about contributing</a> |
    </div>' |

